                                                BUSINESS QUESTIONS 
	Which factor has the strongest relationship with digital wellbeing score? 

                                     QUERY
SELECT
  CORR(daily_screen_time, digital_wellbeing_score) AS screen_corr,
  CORR(sleep_hours, digital_wellbeing_score) AS sleep_corr,
  CORR(anxiety_level, digital_wellbeing_score) AS anxiety_corr
FROM mental_health ;
  
                                       INSIGHT
These shows that the 2 major factors that affect well being are sleep and anxiety, while screen time alone has limited impact.
            
         RECOMMENDATION
This suggests that mental health outcomes are influenced more by emotional and behavioral factors than usage duration.

